body.name: Queen Size Bed Frame with Headboard, Queen Platform Bed Frame with Storage Drawers, Wood Bedframe Queen-Size No Box Spring Needed, Charging Station, Noise Free, Rustic Brown
features: 【ERGONOMIC HEADBOARD FOR ENHANCED COMFORT】 The Kumgang platform bed frame queen size features a specially designed headboard with a 95° tilt, providing superior comfort and support to perfectly fit the natural curve of your back. Relax in ultimate comfort with this ergonomic headboard design.

【3-TIER STORAGE SHELF WITH CHARGING STATION】 Our metal bed frame queen size comes with a wood headboard featuring 3 storage tiers. This provides plenty of space for books, decorations, clocks, or personal items, ensuring everything you need is within easy reach. Additionally, the headboard includes a built-in charging station with 2 AC outlets, 1 USB port, and 1 Type-C charging port for conveniently charging your devices.

【CONVENIENT STORAGE SOLUTION WITH 2 UTILITY DRAWERS】 Say goodbye to clutter and keep your room tidy with the 2 utility drawers of the queen bed frame with headboard. These drawers on wheels are located underneath the footboard for easy access to clothing and bedding with plenty of space. There's also 11.8 inches of space under the bed to store shoes, organizers, luggage, and more.

【NOISE-FREE DESIGN & STRONG FRAME】 Enjoy a peaceful sleeping experience with our noise-free bed frame. The bed frame queen size with headboard is made with a full set of thickened metal support systems and an extra center bar, ensuring stability and 100% avoiding any rocking sensation. The silent foam strips between metal parts prevent friction, allowing you to sleep undisturbed.

【EASY ASSEMBLY & NO BOX SPRING NEEDED】 We prioritize your convenience with our easy assembly process. All parts of the queen bed frame with drawers are included in the package, each part is clearly labeled and numbered, and no extra tools are required. It only takes 45 minutes to assemble accurately. Plus, our frame fits all 8-12 inch mattresses, no box spring needed or any additional foundation, saving you both money and time!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Kumgang Industrial Bed Frame Upgrade your bedroom with this elegant queen size bed frame. The Kumgang Queen Size Bed Frame with Storage Drawers is a stylish and practical addition to any bedroom. Made from high quality wood and a metal frame that provides maximum support and durability to the mattress, you won't have to worry at all about its ability to hold the weight of any size person and mattress.

Charging Station The headboard with 3 tiers of storage shelves has a built-in charging station that includes 2 AC outlets, 1 USB port, and 1 Type-C port for convenient charging of your devices. Ergonomic Headboard The specially designed headboard tilts up to 95° for superior comfort and support, and conforms perfectly to the natural curve of your back.

2 Storage Drawers The 2 drawers under the footboard provide easy access to clothing and bedding, so you can say goodbye to clutter and keep your room tidy. Extra Reinforced Center Bar Features a full set of padded metal support system and extra center bar to ensure stability and 100% avoid rocking sensation.
